<h2>Step-by-Step WooCommerce Installation and Configuration</h2><br>

<p>With planning complete, let's dive into the technical implementation process that will transform your retail business into an online powerhouse.</p>

<img src={infographic} alt="10-Step WooCommerce Launch Process infographic" style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; height: auto; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);" />

<strong>WordPress Foundation Setup</strong>
Start with a reliable Australian hosting provider that offers optimised WordPress hosting. Look for hosts with Australian data centres to ensure fast loading times for local customers. Install WordPress with one-click installers available through most hosting panels.

<strong>WooCommerce Plugin Installation</strong>
Navigate to your WordPress dashboard, go to Plugins > Add New, search for "WooCommerce," and install the official plugin by Automattic. The setup wizard will guide you through initial configuration, including:
<br><ul>
<li>Store location (set to Australia)</li>
<li>Currency (AUD)</li>
<li>Payment methods</li>
<li>Shipping options</li>
<li>Tax settings (including GST)</li>
</ul><br>

<strong>Theme Selection and Customisation</strong>
Choose a WooCommerce-compatible theme that reflects your brand and appeals to Hills District customers. Popular options include:
<br><ul>
<li>Storefront (free, officially supported)</li>
<li>Astra (lightweight, fast-loading)</li>
<li>OceanWP (highly customisable)</li>
</ul><br>

<p>Customise your chosen theme with your brand colours, logo, and imagery that resonates with local customers. Include recognisable Hills District landmarks or references where appropriate to build local connection.</p>

<strong>Essential Plugin Configuration</strong>
Install and configure essential plugins for Australian retailers:
<br><ul>
<li><strong>Australian Post Shipping</strong>: Integrate Australia Post shipping rates</li>
<li><strong>GST/Tax Management</strong>: Ensure proper tax calculation</li>
<li><strong>Payment Gateway Integration</strong>: Connect your preferred payment processors</li>
<li><strong>Security Plugins</strong>: Use SSL certificates and security monitoring</li>
</ul><br>

